<h2 id="-display-of-axie-stats">ğŸ“Œ Display of Axie Stats</h2>

<p>The <strong>Health</strong>, <strong>Speed</strong>, <strong>Skill</strong> and <strong>Morale</strong> stats are displayed below the name of each Axie. The <strong>pureness</strong> in percentage is also shown on the top-right area of each Axie card.</p>

